{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FileSystemSync","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileSystemSync","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileSystemSync\"><code>FileSystemSync</code></a></strong></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>非标准:</strong> 该特性是非标准的，请尽量不要在生产环境中使用它！</p></div>\n<p>在 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/File_API/File_System_API\">文件系统 API</a> 中， <code>FileSystemSync</code> 对象表示文件系统。它有两个属性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"关于这个文档","title":"关于这个文档","isH3":false,"content":"<p>这个文档最后更新与 2012 年 3 月 2 日，并且遵循 <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/file-system-api/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">W3C 规范（工作草案）</a>，起草于 2011 年 4 月 19 日。</p>\n<p>规范目前已废弃，没有得到大量的关注。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本概念","title":"基本概念","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>FileSystemSync</code> 对象是整个 API 的必经之路，你会大量使用它。所以一旦你获得了引用，将对象缓存在全局变量或类属性中。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Attribute</th>\n      <th>Type</th>\n      <th>Description</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>name</code></td>\n      <td><code>只读</code> <code>DOMString</code></td>\n      <td>文件系统的名称。名称在开放的文件系统列表中必须是唯一的。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>root</code></td>\n      <td><code>只读 DirectoryEntry</code></td>\n      <td>文件系统的根目录。</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.FileSystemSync","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileSystemSync/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另见","title":"另见","isH3":false,"content":"<p>规范：<a href=\"https://dev.w3.org/2009/dap/file-system/pub/FileSystem/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">File API: Directories and System Specification</a></p>\n<p>参考： <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/File_API/File_System_API\">文件系统 API</a></p>\n<p>简介：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/File_and_Directory_Entries_API/Introduction\">文件系统 API 的基本概念</a></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"关于这个文档","id":"关于这个文档"},{"text":"基本概念","id":"基本概念"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"另见","id":"另见"}],"summary":"在 文件系统 API 中， FileSystemSync 对象表示文件系统。它有两个属性。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FileSystemSync","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FileSystemSync","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/filesystemsync","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/filesystemsync/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/FileSystemSync","title":"FileSystemSync"}],"pageTitle":"FileSystemSync - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}